columns.name: name
columns.description: The name of the log stream.

columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the log stream.

columns.name: log_group_name
columns.description: The name of the log group, in which the log stream belongs.

columns.name: creation_time
columns.description: The creation time of the log stream.

columns.name: first_event_timestamp
columns.description: The time of the first event.

columns.name: last_event_timestamp
columns.description: The time of the most recent log event in the log stream in CloudWatch Logs.

columns.name: last_ingestion_time
columns.description: Specifies the last log ingestion time.

columns.name: upload_sequence_token
columns.description: Specifies the log upload sequence token.
